{"tid":124230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你會選擇愛你既人，定你愛既人過世？","createTime":"2017-02-17T12:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T12:40:37.000Z","uid":41813,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a63f9999137649b9b70ff1228c4630de6179a35","tid":124230,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"愛人係痛苦<br />\n被愛係幸福<br />\n細細個覺得一定要揀愛你個個<br />\n因為咁樣先會開心<br />\n但隨住人慢慢大個<br />\n就開始覺得人生太短，要盡力去追求你所愛<br />\n人生亦同時太長，無可能屈就自己一世<br />\n人生得一次<br />\n如果係你<br />\n你會揀愛你既<br />\n定係揀你愛既過世<br />\n<br />\n正皮：愛你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮：你愛既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ff288ec0aa53d25c5b013ea358a707f131196e","tid":124230,"uid":14566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},{"pid":"f006aba0f7aed565d499c752f8ecd632846816f7","tid":124230,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Why not both?</blockquote><br />\n如果both到當然最好啦<br />\n但係咪真係咁完美先巴打"},{"pid":"5724e9b370e5501de83a32b84b98547e6cd637ac","tid":124230,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"愛我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad32293a9ead762d6d8368d150d0b4e20199a7a9","tid":124230,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？<br />\n如果唔介意可以試下分享你既故事"}]}